OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,FThousands of people gathered in Truro
OL,7,Ftoday, Saturday 2 August, to celebrate
OL,8,Fdiversity, inclusion and culture.
OL,10,FNow in its fifth year 'Celebration of
OL,11,FCulture', which is organised by Black
OL,12,FVoices Cornwall, is a showcase of
OL,13,Fmusic, international food and lots
OL,14,Fmore.
