OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,FAbi Hutchinson who helped put on the
OL,7,Fevent said: "Five years ago was when
OL,8,Fall the Black Lives Matters movement
OL,9,Fwas happening, and we thought that is
OL,10,Fa really dark and scary place to be in
OL,11,Fand we simply wanted to bring a bit of
OL,12,Flight to the darkness.
OL,14,F"I think to have these events is so
OL,15,Fimportant in Cornwall. Because they
OL,16,Fare so lacking unfortunately.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
