OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,F"Black Voices Cornwall is so well
OL,7,Fplaced to provide that experience for
OL,8,Fpeople that look like me and don't
OL,9,Flook like me and want to enjoy culture
OL,10,Fand have more experience in culture
OL,11,Fand diversity."
OL,13,FMarcus Alleyne helped set up the event
OL,14,Fwhen it first started in 2020.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
