OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,FSpeaking about the first event he
OL,7,Fsaid: "When I think back to the first
OL,8,Fevent, we had maybe a few hundred
OL,9,Fpeople throughout the day, milling
OL,10,Fabout, about half the size and now
OL,11,Fhere we are five years later, I think
OL,12,Fit is just going to get bigger and
OL,13,Fbetter."
OL,15,FHe now leads Rock Choir, who perform
OL,16,Fat the event. He added: "As a black
OL,17,Fmusician in Cornwall to be able to
OL,18,Ffind somewhere where I can identify,
OL,19,Fbe who I am to the fullest in a safe
OL,20,Fspace, that is incredible."
