OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,FBev Bevington is a stall holder at the
OL,7,Fevent, speaking about why she takes
OL,8,Fpart, she said: "I just like the idea
OL,9,Fof being able to celebrate bringing
OL,10,Fpeople together and having a day to
OL,11,Fexchange what we know about each other
OL,12,Fand ourselves."
OL,14,FRichard Edoki is a community hospital
OL,15,Fpresenter. He came to the event last
OL,16,Fyear and introduced himself to
OL,17,Forganisers. This year he is DJing at
OL,18,Fthe event, he says representing people
OL,19,Fof Africa.
