OL,3,C'I can be who I am': How a celebration
OL,4,Cof culture brings people together
OL,6,FHe added: "Music is a platform that
OL,7,Funites people. It helps bring peace to
OL,8,Fthe community."
OL,10,FSisi Cherinet has opened what she
OL,11,Fbelieves is the first beauty salon for
OL,12,Fafro hair in Truro. She said: "It
OL,13,Fmeans a lot, we are celebrating
OL,14,Fculture today, which hair is a part of.
OL,16,F"As you can see it is not only hair,
OL,17,Fthere's lots of things around us and
OL,18,Fwe can learn a lot from each other.
OL,19,FIt's important to interact with the
OL,20,Fcommunity and create bonds."
